org.redpin.base.core
Class Measurement

java.lang.Object
  org.redpin.base.core.Measurement
Direct Known Subclasses:
Measurement, Measurement
public abstract class Measurement
extends java.lang.Object

Describes a measurement containing several readings from the bluetooth-, wifi- and gsm device. When extending it, you have to implement IMeasurement

Version:
0.2
Author:
Philipp Bolliger (philipp@bolliger.name), Simon Tobler (simon.p.tobler@gmx.ch), Pascal Brogle (broglep@student.ethz.ch)
